{"tid":1153832,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【超人退休】撤資定為交棒？李嘉誠賣走中港2,000億資產","createTime":"2019-05-14T01:28:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T13:56:19.000Z","uid":66811,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3197fb4c5e35d23ec3b88b2327ec787bdec59367","tid":1153832,"uid":66811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T01:28:18.000Z","msg":"誠哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180317/57957224\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180317%2F57957224&d=4exhEwVElvs0p929i6aHTxjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=23e9729b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180317%2F57957224&h=813c85df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180317/57957224</a><br />\n<br />\n2014年9月本港政治形勢急轉直下，「佔中運動」展開，官媒《新華社》10月發文批評李嘉誠等多名富豪，未響應國家主席習近平號召反佔中，似乎令李嘉誠加快撤資舉動。2015年1月，李嘉誠違「永不遷冊」承諾，旗下兩大上市旗艦長實及和黃重組合併後，分拆出地產業務，亦即是長和及長實地產（1113），註冊地不再選擇香港，而是離岸金融中心開曼群島，李澤鉅解釋僅為做生意方便，又指商業登記及上市地均在香港。<br />\n<br />\n包括官媒在內多間媒體同年發文炮轟李嘉誠，指他「過橋抽板」，「利用特權在內地賺錢，內地經濟遇困難時卻離開」，最終李嘉誠公開聲明反擊官媒，又解釋沽售資產，回報是回到股東手裏；而減持地產是因為內地供求失衡風險，不等於不投資內地。"},{"pid":"89382e2f9e30e0dcc5c81f57f646d2e9efb8e5cb","tid":1153832,"uid":253005,"like":3,"dislike":26,"score":-23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T01:29:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9538eacfae853067216c177a2056d40f28188648","tid":1153832,"uid":201604,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T01:29:11.000Z","msg":"daddy話要套現啲現金買生日禮物畀我"},{"pid":"0455f417c7892f6b065c3f8253918440226dd57b","tid":1153832,"uid":66811,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"89382e2f9e30e0dcc5c81f57f646d2e9efb8e5cb","tid":1153832,"uid":253005,"like":3,"dislike":26,"score":-23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T01:29:11.000Z"